Laura M. Russell, Appellee, v. New York Life Insurance Company, Appellant.Gen. No. 9,509.

(Abstract of Decision.)

Heard in this court at February term, 1940;opinion filed April 26, 1940;rehearing denied June 5, 1940.Scott, Macleish & Falk and Miller, Elliott & Westervelt, for appellant; John D. Thomason, of counsel; Knoblock & Sloan, for appellee; John F. Sloan, Jr., of counsel. Opinion by Presiding Justice Wolfe.
